          Login
        </a>
        <a href="cadastroaluno" class="primary-gradient text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-extrabold text-lg shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20 hover:opacity-90 transition-transform active:scale-100 scale-95">
          Começar Agora
        </a>
      </nav>

    </nav>
  </header>

  <main class="pt-24 min-h-screen">

    <!-- ===================== HERO ===================== -->
    <section class="relative px-8 py-16 md:py-24 overflow-hidden" aria-labelledby="suporte-heading">

      <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center relative z-10">

        <!-- Badge de status -->
        <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-surface-container-high mb-8">
          <b class="flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-green-500 animate-pulse font-normal" aria-hidden="true"></b>
          <em class="text-sm font-semibold text-on-surface-variant not-italic">Todos os sistemas operacionais</em>
        </p>

        <h1 id="suporte-heading" class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black tracking-tighter text-on-surface mb-8 leading-none">
          Como podemos <em class="text-primary italic">ajudar?</em>
        </h1>

        <!-- Barra de busca -->
        <search class="relative group max-w-2xl mx-auto block">
          <label for="busca-suporte" class="sr-only">Pesquisar suporte</label>
          <i class="material-symbols-outlined text-outline absolute inset-y-0 left-6 flex items-center pointer-events-none not-italic" style="display:flex;align-items:center;" aria-hidden="true">search</i>
          <input
            id="busca-suporte"
            type="search"
            placeholder="Pesquise por temas, dúvidas ou tutoriais..."
            class="w-full pl-16 pr-8 py-6 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-full border-none shadow-xl shadow-on-surface/5 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary transition-all text-lg font-medium placeholder:text-outline"
          />
          <button type="submit" class="absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-primary text-on-primary px-8 py-3 rounded-full font-bold hover:bg-primary-dim transition-colors">
            Buscar
          </button>
        </search>

      </article>

      <!-- Elementos decorativos de fundo -->
      <b class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-primary/5 rounded-full blur-3xl block font-normal" aria-hidden="true"></b>
      <b class="absolute -bottom-24 -left-24 w-96 h-96 bg-tertiary-container/10 rounded-full blur-3xl block font-normal" aria-hidden="true"></b>

    </section>

    <!-- ===================== CATEGORIAS ===================== -->
    <section class="px-8 py-16 bg-surface-container-low" aria-labelledby="categorias-heading">
      <h2 id="categorias-heading" class="sr-only">Categorias de suporte</h2>

      <article class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6" role="list">

          <!-- Card: Meu Plano -->
          <li class="group p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-3xl hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/20 hover:-translate-y-2">
            <figure class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary-container/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">
              <i class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl group-hover:text-white not-italic" aria-hidden="true">account_circle</i>
            </figure>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-white">Meu Plano</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant group-hover:text-white/80 text-sm">Gerencie sua assinatura, renovações e upgrades.</p>
          </li>

          <!-- Card: Acesso e Login -->
          <li class="group p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-3xl hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/20 hover:-translate-y-2">
            <figure class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary-container/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">
              <i class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl group-hover:text-white not-italic" aria-hidden="true">lock_open</i>
            </figure>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-white">Acesso e Login</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant group-hover:text-white/80 text-sm">Problemas para entrar? Recupere sua senha aqui.</p>
          </li>

          <!-- Card: Pagamentos -->
          <li class="group p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-3xl hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/20 hover:-translate-y-2">
            <figure class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary-container/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">
              <i class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl group-hover:text-white not-italic" aria-hidden="true">payments</i>
            </figure>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-white">Pagamentos</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant group-hover:text-white/80 text-sm">Faturas, métodos de pagamento e reembolsos.</p>
          </li>

          <!-- Card: Treinos e Professores -->
          <li class="group p-8 bg-surface-container-lowest rounded-3xl hover:bg-primary transition-all duration-300 cursor-pointer shadow-sm hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-primary/20 hover:-translate-y-2">
            <figure class="w-14 h-14 rounded-2xl bg-primary-container/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-white/20 transition-colors">
              <i class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl group-hover:text-white not-italic" aria-hidden="true">exercise</i>
            </figure>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold mb-2 group-hover:text-white">Treinos e Professores</h3>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant group-hover:text-white/80 text-sm">Dúvidas sobre rotinas, exercícios e mentores.</p>
          </li>

        </ul>
      </article>
    </section>

    <!-- ===================== FAQ ===================== -->
    <section class="px-8 py-24" aria-labelledby="faq-heading">
      <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

        <header class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-8 mb-16">
          <section>
            <h2 id="faq-heading" class="font-headline text-4xl font-black tracking-tight text-on-surface mb-4">Perguntas Frequentes</h2>
            <p class="font-body text-on-surface-variant text-lg">As respostas mais rápidas para suas dúvidas cotidianas.</p>
          </section>
          <a href="#" class="text-primary font-bold flex items-center gap-2 group font-headline">
            Ver todo o FAQ
            <i class="material-symbols-outlined transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1 not-italic" aria-hidden="true">arrow_forward</i>
          </a>
        </header>

        <ul class="space-y-4" role="list">

          <!-- FAQ 1 -->
          <li>
            <details class="group bg-surface-container rounded-3xl overflow-hidden [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
              <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-8 cursor-pointer select-none">
                <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface">Como faço para cancelar minha assinatura?</h3>
                <i class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 not-italic" aria-hidden="true">expand_more</i>
              </summary>
              <p class="px-8 pb-8 font-body text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                Você pode cancelar sua assinatura a qualquer momento através das configurações de perfil em "Assinatura". O acesso permanecerá ativo até o final do período já pago. Não há taxas de cancelamento ocultas.
              </p>
            </details>
          </li>

          <!-- FAQ 2 -->
          <li>
            <details class="group bg-surface-container rounded-3xl overflow-hidden [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
              <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-8 cursor-pointer select-none">
                <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface">Posso treinar em mais de um dispositivo ao mesmo tempo?</h3>
                <i class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180 not-italic" aria-hidden="true">expand_more</i>
              </summary>
              <p class="px-8 pb-8 font-body text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
                Sim, o PlanoB permite que você acesse sua conta em múltiplos dispositivos. No entanto, dependendo do seu plano, pode haver um limite de transmissões simultâneas de vídeos de treino.
              </p>
            </details>
          </li>

          <!-- FAQ 3 -->
          <li>
            <details class="group bg-surface-container rounded-3xl overflow-hidden [&_summary::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
              <summary class="flex items-center justify-between p-8 cursor-pointer select-none">
                <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-on-surface">Como altero meu método de pagamento?</h3>
